cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about video prediction, which involves analyzing and generating visual data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also proposes a novel approach using LSTM and convolutional neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves predicting the future, which is a common task in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed model also has potential applications in robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
